<C>__{john}
<D>__{and a car.}
<C>__{jill}
<D>__{john, i'm so proud of you.}
<A>__{john pauses, looks at her.}
<C>__{john}
<D>__{what's the matter? you don't like your food?}
<A>__{the maitre d' has come up to the table. john stops suddenly. they are both very chagrined.}
<C>__{maitre d'}
