<A>__{carol o.s. puts the phone down. then there is silence on the other end. the crowd of people around jill and john begin to shuffle and murmur. john tries to keep them quiet while listening into the phone. then two policemen come forward through the crowd. one of them kneels down to john and jill who are still on the floor.}
